{
  "stem": "26142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it had a turbine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and that's how-- that's how-- and it worked 24 hours, day and night.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even winter time, where there-- most of the river would-- would freeze sometimes, but there was enough water where we had the mill, that there was enough water to drive-- to drive it.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Very-- I don't remember it ever being stopped in winter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- my father lost a lot of money.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In 1929, I was nine years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we paid-- we paid 100 or 120 krones for a cubic meter of lumber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And two years later, in 1930, '31, when the-- when the depression came, you couldn't sell it for 40 krone, for a third.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and what the trouble was, that you had thousands of cubic meters of lumber laying out by the river.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And a-- a-- there was like a-- a-- it's not a microbe-- some kind of a-- a-- thing would get into the-- into the trees.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It wasn't a bacteria.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was green.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was like-- like a-- how-- how-- like a little worm, green worms.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, you know, and-- and-- and it-- it would already-- it would already-- and if it laid for-- for two years, summer and winter out there, it deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the quality deteriorated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was-- that was the-- the problem.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The first effects of the war we started to feel in 1935-- '34, '35.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the first two families that-- that escaped from Germany in 1945-- '35-- from-- the two families were from Frankfurt am Main.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember they came to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How they came to Torun, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I remember one family stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
